Date: 0/0/1986
Source: Speaking for Ourselves
Author: OWEN & PERKINS
Vol / Page: 68
Edition:
Quote: Different things brought people together to swag. There was I, on my Pat Malone, starting off on my first experience at humping a swag.
Notes:  (Bob Edwards, bushman)
